data.description: Welcome to 14403 Otis Court! This charming one level 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom house offers a spacious layout and desirable features, this property offers a wonderful opportunity for families and individuals alike. It has been freshly painted and has new luxury vinyl plank flooring installed throughout. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a lovely porch, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or relaxing in the evening. As you step inside, the cozy fireplace catches your eye, providing warmth and comfort during colder months. The house also boasts a deck and patio, ideal for hosting gatherings or simply unwinding outdoors. While the pool is currently in need of renovation, it presents an exciting project for those with a knack for design and a desire to create their own personal oasis. Newer roof with lifetime warranty. Conveniently located near shopping centers and dining options, this home offers easy access to all your daily needs. Commuting is a breeze as well, with major routes just moments away.  With 2046 square feet of living space, there's plenty of room for everyone to spread out and make themselves at home. The four bedrooms provide ample space for rest and relaxation, while the two bathrooms ensure convenience and privacy.  Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make 14403 Otis Court your own. Schedule a showing today and discover the potential that awaits within these walls!
